        "filename": "eval_workorder_internal.txt",
        "source_type": "txt",
        "groups": ["eval-group"],
        "chunks": [
          "劳动合同续签工单系统需求说明：HR在工单系统中发起续签申请，合同组内部审核并盖章归档。该材料用于内部审批流配置。"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "eval-doc-form-noise",
        "title": "全职员工入职人员信息表",
        "filename": "eval_form_noise.xlsx",
        "source_type": "xlsx",
        "groups": ["eval-group"],
        "chunks": [
          "表格数据 A1:员工姓名 B1:劳动合同起始日 C1:劳动合同终止日。全职员工入职人员信息表。"
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "eval-doc-shanghai-social-security-table",
        "title": "上海社保公积金截止时间表",
        "filename": "eval_shanghai_social_security_table.xlsx",
        "source_type": "xlsx",
        "groups": ["eval-group"],
        "chunks": [
